  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THUNDER HELIX</strong> Pilot deadly helicopter gunships, battle enemy forces and complete dangerous missions within a thrilling desert warzone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting campaign with multiple objectives,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or play randomised scenarios.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pilot multiple types of helicopter with unique abilities and specifications.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up ammo, fuel and rescue friendlies with the on-board winch.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missions take place in dawn, day and night-time environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crisp 320 x 200 resolution with 4, 16 or 256 color graphics. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explosive camels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flight Control Options:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flight Joystick</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse Flight + Keyboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or Keyboard Only</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906230/extras/d8b26fa98432f25eb403e71ee1a474f8.avif?t=1772186335\" width=640 height=148 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THUNDER HELIX</strong> Pilot deadly helicopter gunships, battle enemy forces and complete dangerous missions within a thrilling desert warzone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting campaign with multiple objectives,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or play randomised scenarios.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pilot multiple types of helicopter with unique abilities and specifications.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up ammo, fuel and rescue friendlies with the on-board winch.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missions take place in dawn, day and night-time environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crisp 320 x 200 resolution with 4, 16 or 256 color graphics. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explosive camels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flight Control Options:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flight Joystick</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse Flight + Keyboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or Keyboard Only</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1906230/extras/d8b26fa98432f25eb403e71ee1a474f8.avif?t=1772186335\" width=640 height=148 /></span></p>",
